metadata.name: Bird Of The Mind
metadata.description:
In this painting, the bird of the human mind is captured by her own thoughts and beliefs. The only way to release this bird is that she must open her mind and expand her vision to break this bond.

---------------------------------------------------------

This painting is inspired  by my inner world and I drew all the lines in the moment . (completely free hand)
Manual and Digital painting
